"  urpm media add https://mirrors.mageia.org/mageia/9/x86_64/media/core/"
"release/\n"
"\n"
"For custom/third-party media, use --custom with name and short_name:\n"
"  urpm media add --custom \"My Repo\" myrepo https://example.com/repo/"
"x86_64/\n"
"\n"
"For legacy mode (non-Mageia URL with explicit name):\n"
"  urpm media add --name \"My Media\" https://example.com/repo/\n"
msgstr ""
"Een mediabron toevoegen.\n"
"\n"
"Voor officiële Mageia-media hoeft u alleen de URL op te geven:\n"
"  urpm media add https://mirrors.mageia.org/mageia/9/x86_64/media/core/"
"release/\n"
"\n"
"Voor aangepaste/externe media gebruikt u --custom met naam en verkorte "
"naam:\n"
"  urpm media add --custom \"Mijn Repo\" mijnrepo https://example.com/repo/"
"x86_64/\n"
"\n"
"Voor de verouderde modus (niet-Mageia URL met expliciete naam):\n"
"  urpm media add --name \"Mijn Media\" https://example.com/repo/\n"

